WHAT A 1915 hipped-roof frame house with three bedrooms, two full bathrooms and two half bathrooms
HOW MUCH $249,500
SIZE 2,136 square feet
PRICE PER SQUARE FOOT $117
SETTING The property is on a tree-lined street filled with vintage homes, on the southeast side of Cedar Rapids, several blocks from Bever Park, which has a public swimming pool and a children’s zoo with farm animals.
